:white_check_mark: Issue solved by accessing to this url <https://api.hubapi.com/crm-object-schemas/v3/schemas/{objectId}?portalId={portalId]&hapikey={apiKey>], where your portalId and objectId can be found in network inspector of your browser when loading the page of your custom object
